* PHAVerLite 0.6
  Requires PPLite 0.10.2 (which fixes a bug on NNC polyhedra).

* PHAVerLite 0.5
  Requires PPLite 0.8
  New command id1.is_intersecting(id2)

* PHAVerLite 0.4
  Requires PPLite 0.7
  Uses by default boxed polyhedra (when using sets of polyhedra).
  New command line option -p=<POLY_KIND> enables to choose among
  different instances of PPLite polyhedra (Poly, F_Poly, ...),
  defaulting to Poly.

* PHAVerLite 0.3.1 (fixes bug in 0.3)
  Requires PPLite 0.6
  Uses by default boxed polyhedra (when using sets of polyhedra).
  New command line option -p=F_Poly enables the domain of "factored"
  polyhedra (experimental feature, not fully optimized).

* PHAVerLite 0.2.1
  Requires PPLite 0.5.1
  Bug corrected in Poly::parallel_affine_image()

* PHAVerLite 0.2
  Requires PPLite 0.5
  Uses by default boxed polyhedra (when using sets of polyhedra).

* PHAVerLite 0.1
